{"tid":1318005,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港台大不同】台灣民眾大街打水戰 公然攞水喉直射警員","createTime":"2019-07-15T00:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T00:55:04.000Z","uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"94c3d7b6c2c899e3c98ef0d93a94dc071f8c9f8f","tid":1318005,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T00:35:08.000Z","msg":"【港台大不同】民眾大街打水戰 公然攞水喉直射警員<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190714/large/1563098775_e9b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190714%2Flarge%2F1563098775_e9b0.jpg&h=782ac78c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港的警民關係緊張，警員向和平示威者出動警棍驅散，甚至亂噴胡椒噴霧及發射橡膠子彈，但反觀台灣，民眾則可與警員一起同樂，宜蘭蘇澳昨日舉行「瘋冷泉打水戰」活動，民眾在大街上打水戰，有民眾拿公然的拿水喉直噴騎着電單車的警員，網民大讚：「天熱幫警消消暑，好貼心！」<br />\n<br />\n網民在fb社團上載照片，顯示一名騎電單車的蘇澳警員，<span style=\"color: red;\">被民眾拿着水喉，當着臉部狂噴，警員當下被涼一下，也露出笑容。</span>旁邊的民眾則拿着水槍、水桶在打水仗。<br />\n<br />\n這次活動是蘇澳鎮公所舉辦，目的是為當地旅遊宣傳，但很多網民都指這張警民同樂的照片相當有趣，說：「讚！平常沒人敢這樣吧！」「唯一可以公然襲警的機會！」亦有網民稱：「反擊叫消防車來！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190714/59823073\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190714%2F59823073&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKae24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=1aa0b994\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190714%2F59823073&h=8f52b629\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190714/59823073</a>"},{"pid":"93d7bdf1595105ac9d319901ec062911c78ea350","tid":1318005,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T00:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51616a5cb05a9cb82d810af9ce6432b6d5d1692b","tid":1318005,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T00:55:04.000Z","msg":"香港潑水節都會咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}